  shakespeare uses the image of proteus to establish the character of his great royal villain richard iii in the play henry vi , part three , in which the future usurper boasts :   shakespeare also names one of the main characters of his play the two gentlemen of verona proteus .

shakespeare 's opening lines : valentine:"cease to persuade , my loving proteus ; home - keeping youth have ever homely wits "

